{"author":"Joe Oakhart","data":{"alias":"gross-muck-gripe","description":"## What\n\n**Cut the reconciler over** to the self-healing ref-lock (C1+C2) and stop writing coordination\nstate into the tickets working tree.\n\n- Rewire `acquire_pass_lock`/`release_pass_lock` and the phase-gate in\n  `src/rebar/_engine/rebar_reconciler/_advisory_lock.py:243,302,69-70` to use `_ref_lock` on\n  `refs/reconciler/lock` and `refs/reconciler/gate` instead of `_write_file_to_tickets_branch`.\n- Update the pass orchestration in `src/rebar/_engine/rebar_reconciler/__main__.py:373-447`\n  (Steps 2a pass-lock, 2b phase-gate, 3 acquire/run/`finally`-release) to drive the ref-lock and\n  to **heartbeat** (`renew()` at ~lease/3) across the running pass.\n- Stop creating `.reconciler-pass-lock` / `.reconciler-phase-gate` in the tickets tree entirely.\n- The authoritative ref lives on `origin` (`sync.remote`); acquire/renew/release push the ref via\n  `--force-with-lease=<ref>:<old>` (explicit lease ref form, never bare).\n\nScope note: this child keeps the old `merge=ours`/`.gitattributes` entry and the `b859` retry loop\nin place (removed in the final child) so this change is bisectable on its own.\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n\n- [ ] `_advisory_lock.acquire_pass_lock`/`release_pass_lock` + phase-gate use `_ref_lock` over\n      `refs/reconciler/*`; no `.reconciler-pass-lock`/`.reconciler-phase-gate` is written to the\n      tickets branch.\n- [ ] `rebar_reconciler/__main__.py` acquires, heartbeats at ~lease/3 during the pass, and\n      releases in a `finally`; a crashed pass (no release) is reclaimable after lease expiry.\n- [ ] Remote coordination pushes the ref with explicit `--force-with-lease=<ref>:<old>`.\n- [ ] Idempotency asserted: a test that runs two overlapping passes (forced double-acquire) shows\n      the reconciler still converges (efficiency-lock invariant holds).\n- [ ] Non-integration suite green.","id":"2711-21bf-ab71-4136","parent_id":"6c9c-811f-6dc4-40e7","priority":2,"tags":[],"ticket_type":"task","title":"Cut reconciler pass-lock/phase-gate over to refs/reconciler/* (stop tree-committing locks)"},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"CREATE","timestamp":1783216081277812001,"uuid":"424d9809-7883-42ae-9679-cfadc3169e4b"}